import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css";
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card'

function RepoCard(){
    <Card>
    <Card.Body>
        <Card.Title>Repo name</Card.Title>
        <Card.Text>
            Repo descriptio

        </Card.Text>
        <Card.Link href=''>repo url</Card.Link>

    </Card.Body>

</Card>

}
export default RepoCard;
